<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA80">
<l>niṉṟeti rāya niraimaṇittēr vāṇaṉṟō</l>
<l>ḷoṉṟiyavī raiññū ṟuṭaṉṟuṇiya – veṉṟilaṅku</l>
<l>mārpaṭuvā ṉēmi yaravaṇaiyāṉ cēvaṭikkē</l>
<l>nērpaṭuvāṉ ṟāṉmuyalu neñcu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The red feet of him on the serpent bed, with the sharpened white discus</l>
<l>that shines victoriously when the combined twice five hundred arms of Bāṇa</l>
<l>are cut all together, who had stood up against [him] on a chariot with jewels in rows ,</l>
<l>[my] heart strains to get close [to them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
